data.description: Price Reudced!! Take note NO HOA FEES !! This amazing Siesta Key oasis is modern and stylish.  It has plenty of parking for your out-of-town guests and no HOA!  The new roof and gutters help the crisp, updated Navy paint impart a Nautical feel. From the moment you step inside, you will notice lots of Natural light, modern neutral paint color, open feeling and pristine condition of the immaculate island home. The oversized screened-in Lanai, accessed by 2 large French doors, adds a huge amount of entertainment area and even the possibility of a Spa.  This home features a large open living room, dining room, new kitchen and new Kitchen-aide appliances. Master bedroom is spacious with a walk-in closet and beautiful, sleek private bath. The second bedroom is good sized as well and both bedrooms have ceiling fans. Bonus room could be used for as an office, TV room, or even extra room for guests and has it's own private outside entrance. The laundry room has Maytag washer and dryer that comes with a warranty. With its entrance from Treasure Boat Way, the newly fenced back yard includes a double wide gate to give you flexibility to store your "toys".  The shelled back yard, with the island vibe, is easy to maintain. Near to downtown Siesta Key restaurants and shopping Upgrades include new roof, new electrical panel, new PEX interior plumbing, new fence, and new landscaping. Some Windows were replaced and have a 10 year transferrable warranty. There is also a transferrable wildlife contract and termite contract. Sarasota County provides the Public Utilities of sewer, water and trash. Florida Power & Light provides the electricity. Give this island home a look to fully appreciate it's appeal. You won't be disappointed when you view this home!!
